article.description: — Donovan Sims scored 14 points, Josh Jefferson added 12, and Middle Tennessee defeated Florida International 50-39 on Saturday.
article.headline: Sims, Jefferson lead Middle Tennessee past FIU
article.linkText: Sims, Jefferson lead Middle Tennessee past FIU
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — Donovan Sims scored 14 points, Josh Jefferson added 12, and Middle Tennessee defeated Florida International 50-39 on Saturday. Eli Lawrence added 10 rebounds for the Blue Raiders (11-6, 2-2 C-USA). Clevon Brown had seven points and eight rebounds for the Panthers (10-7, 0-4). —-
